<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7614> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7614" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "A senator who was proscribed in 43,(App. BC 4.27, #). Probably not identifiable with L. Flaminius (7), but might be a Vettius, an Annius, a Toranius, or a Magius, or, if the cognomen was really Gillo, a Fulvius (RS, MS 55-60-RP 1.270).\n" .
